ref=\"http://http//www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-27585310\">Frozen became the highest-grossing animated film</a> of all time, as well as the highest-grossing musical, ahead of The Lion King and Mamma Mia! It currently stands at number 5 <a href=\"http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/\">in the list of all time grossers</a>, with a worldwide total of $1.3bn. It also won Oscars for best animation and best song (for Let It Go) in 2014. Disney’s intention to extend the life of the Frozen characters became clear, with the planned release of seven minute short, Frozen Fever, featuring Anna, Elsa, Kristoff and snowman Olaf.</p> <p>No details are yet available as to Frozen 2’s planned release date.</p>","headline":"Frozen 2 officially announced","trailText":"Disney’s hugely successful Oscar-winning animation has sequel greenlit, with Jennifer Lee and Chris Buck attached","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/3/12/1426184007625/e8872be7-1b09-4952-add2-6c9e34780b3e-140x84.jpeg","wordcount":"179","commentable":"true","byline":"Andrew Pulver","productionOffice":"UK","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2015-03-15T18:15:00+00:00"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/mar/12/frozen-2-sequel-disney-to-be-let-go-jennifer-lee-chris-buck","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/film/2015/mar/12/frozen-2-sequel-disney-to-be-let-go-jennifer-lee-chris-buck","sectionName":"Film","tags":[{"id":"film/frozen","webTitle":"Frozen","type":"keyword","sectionId":"film","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/frozen","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/film/frozen","sectionName":"Film","references":[]},{"id":"film/animation","webTitle":"Animation","type":"keyword","sectionId":"film","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/animation","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/film/animation","sectionName":"Film","references":[]},{"id":"film/oscars","webTitle":"Oscars","type":"keyword","sectionId":"film","webUrl":"http://w